- changed version to 0.9.9b

Jan  2, 2002: Jordi Mallach <jordi@sindominio.net>
- Spanish update

Dec 30, 2001: Ludwig Nussel <l-n@users.sourceforge.net>
- changed textentries to comboboxes for q3/wolf protocol selection

